\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190326095334T1r0u2BOAGCXbhx3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903260953351MdzgyZbFUp3Llq0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190326095336rulKGLp7bBNqAt8Z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190326095336LcA2CdsKwOoeY7SU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190326095337J3Vt7DRYhx08MlaT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190326095335aKuv5C1jdPkmQRwb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>题图来自&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mep-fr.org/event/coco-capitan/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Coco Capitán 巴黎个展“Busy Living”</a>&nbsp;<br></p>"}